<lb ed="L" n="0288a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">室中垂代</cb:mulu><head>室中垂代</head>
<lb ed="L" n="0288a02"/><p xml:id="pL155p0288a0201">問僧認著依肰還不是瑞嵒因甚喚主人公
<lb ed="L" n="0288a03"/>代云碓搗東南磨推西北。</p>
<lb ed="L" n="0288a04"/><p xml:id="pL155p0288a0401">問僧萬法歸一一歸何處無對代云大海若
<lb ed="L" n="0288a05"/>不納百川應倒流。</p>
<lb ed="L" n="0288a06"/><p xml:id="pL155p0288a0601">問僧作何行業底人通身紅爛僧云喫官酒
<lb ed="L" n="0288a07"/>臥官街師笑云紅即<anchor xml:id="beg_a0" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_a0"/>紅爛即未爛。</p>
<lb ed="L" n="0288a08"/><p xml:id="pL155p0288a0801">一日問眾合眼許你跳黃河設若開眼時作
<lb ed="L" n="0288a09"/>麼生過無對時有僧問師合眼跳黃河時如
<lb ed="L" n="0288a10"/>何師云無人孟浪過你設若開眼時作麼生
<lb ed="L" n="0288a11"/>過師展手云了又有僧問如前師云今朝霧
<lb ed="L" n="0288a12"/>起答後語云日出後看取復有問如前師云
<lb ed="L" n="0288a13"/>露柱撞翻燈籠答後語云聖僧歸堂打坐。</p>
<lb ed="L" n="0288a14"/><p xml:id="pL155p0288a1401">有時云既是雲門六不收因甚又道北斗裏
<lb ed="L" n="0288a15"/>藏身。</p>
<pb ed="L" xml:id="L155.1643.0288b" n="0288b"/>
<lb ed="L" n="0288b01"/><p xml:id="pL155p0288b0101">有時云髑髏無識道眼精明漢因甚仰面不
<lb ed="L" n="0288b02"/>見天低頭不見地。</p>
<lb ed="L" n="0288b03"/><p xml:id="pL155p0288b0301">有時云拄杖拂子隨我者隨之東南羅漢天
<lb ed="L" n="0288b04"/>王確住者苑住西北去住不隨風力轉無傷
<lb ed="L" n="0288b05"/>物義若為宣。</p>
<lb ed="L" n="0288b06"/><p xml:id="pL155p0288b0601">有時云本來無位次不用強安排山門因甚
<lb ed="L" n="0288b07"/>在前佛殿因甚在後。</p>
<lb ed="L" n="0288b08"/><p xml:id="pL155p0288b0801">有時云十方同聚會箇箇學無為因甚無為
<lb ed="L" n="0288b09"/>無事人尤是金鎻難。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="L" n="0288b10"/><cb:juan fun="close" n="14"><cb:jhead>天童弘覺忞禪師語錄卷第十四</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="L" n="0288b11"/><cb:div type="w"><head>音釋</head>
<lb ed="L" n="0288b12"/><cb:div type="note"><entry><form>薶</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL155p0288b1202" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">與埋同藏也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>噴</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL155p0288b1208" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">普悶切音湓叱也鼓鼻也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form><term rend="no_nor"><g ref="#CB03559">䲭</g></term></form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL155p0288b1219" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">常支切音匙鶗鵳也鶗鵳
<lb ed="L" n="0288b13"/>鷂別名</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>磕</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL155p0288b1305" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">丘蓋切音<term rend="no_nor">嘅</term>兩石相擊聲</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>髑髏</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL155p0288b1317" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">上杜骨切音獨下即侯切音樓
<lb ed="L" n="0288b14"/>頓顱謂之髑髏</note>。</p></cb:def></entry></cb:div></cb:div>
